      "text": [
        " بَنَاتِ أُخْتٍ وَ جَدٍّ قَالَ \"لِبَنَاتِ اَلْأُخْتِ اَلثُّلُثُ وَ مَا بَقِيَ فَلِلْجَدِّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5648 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Sa'd ibn Abi Khalaf from one of the companions of Abu Abdullah (as) regarding the case of daughters of a sister and a grandfather.\nImam (as) said: \"The daughters of the sister receive one-third of the inheritance, and the remainder goes to the grandfather.\""
        ]
      }
